@Jahuty I had the same problem, but found out this new crack puts saves in a different spot. I found the old save folder, moved the files, and the saves loaded up. The original location was C:Program Data3DMGame205100

I moved it to DocumentsMy GamesDishonoredDishonoredGameStorage and it loaded up. This new crack moves the save games for some reason.

To all the people complaining about crashes try running malware scans. I haven't had a single crash yet and I'm 3/4 through the game running at 60FPS.
